Global Internet of Things Insect Detection Lamp Market Insights
Internet of Things Insect Detection Lamp Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Internet of Things Insect Detection Lamp Market Overview
The global Internet of Things (IoT) insect detection lamp market has witnessed rapid growth due to increasing demand for smart solutions in pest control across various industries. As of 2023, the market is valued at USD 2.5 billion and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 15% from 2024 to 2030. The integration of IoT technology with insect detection lamps offers enhanced monitoring and control, providing users with real-time data for more efficient pest management. This market is largely driven by growing agricultural concerns, the rise of smart cities, and demand for eco-friendly pest control solutions.

